{"title": "How do I check the OPV status in Patient Details?", "body": "Follow these steps check the OPV status in Patient Details:\nOpen the patient record\nMake sure you are in the Details tab\nClick Settings\nNavigate to the \"i\" icon next to the OPV button\nHover your mouse over the icon\nWhen the cursor changes into a Finger Pointer, the details of the last OPV results will pop-out next to the icon\nThe results will display whether the OPV check was Completed or if it Failed (see example images below)\n\nThe OPV status check is now complete."}